## Robot hardware requirement 
The robot must satifsfy the following requirements
<li>
<ol>Ultrasonic sensor is mounted on a medium motor and located at the front of the robot</ol>
<ol>Ultrasonic sensor is able to rotate from -90 degree to 90 degree unobstructed</ol>
<ol>Ultrasonic sensor is should be mounted near on the center of of robot's wheel axis</ol>
<ol>Light sensor is mounted on a medium motor can able to rotate and face the ground or forward</ol>
<ol>The track length of the robot should be under 17cm</ol>
</li>	